{"type":null,"faqId":34094,"title":" How do I set a screen unlock pattern?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>Go to </span><span class=\"s2\">Settings</span><span> and touch </span><span class=\"s2\">Privacy &amp; security</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s2\">Security</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s2\">Screen security</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s2\">Screen lock</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s2\">Pattern</span><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>On the </span><span class=\"s2\">Draw an unlock pattern</span><span> screen, swipe your finger across the screen to connect four or more dots together in a pattern and touch </span><span class=\"s2\">Continue</span><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>Draw the pattern again and touch </span><span class=\"s2\">Confirm</span><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>Enter your backup PIN and touch </span><span class=\"s2\">Continue</span><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>Enter your backup PIN again and touch </span><span class=\"s2\">OK</span><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><a name=\"_Toc413916469\"><span>When you power on your phone or press the power button to turn on the screen, the unlock screen is displayed by default. You can then draw the pattern to unlock the screen.</span></a>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":244,"languageName":"mm","faqCode":"8794","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436779656000,"seriesProductName":"CHC-U01","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"CHC-U01,G play mini","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}